lilostitch99
Singapore River, Singapore
2630
Reviewed August 21, 2018
via mobile
Simply delish
Cab a taxi from hotel ( near Han river) for 25dong.
The eatery is situated in a bright alley - walk all the way in. A lot of local and foreigners.
No menu, no order required, just find a table and sit. The staff was super efficient and friendly despite spoke little English.
Find yourself a table; sit and viola!
The staff will bring you the “ standard delish food of screwed porks, a plate of herbs/greens, rice paper, sauce, ban xeo” and together with grilled beef, and beef bun cha noodles. Non beef eater- you can decline the beef bundle.
It was a lovely - tasty “ affordable” meal- importantly not as oily as it looks as I dapped with tissue paper to check on the oil level.
Great choice! Below 130dong without beef dishes. Yes, a satisfied “ feeling full” meal!
Show less
Date of visit: August 2018
