SwizerlandRoisinDubh
Montreux, Switzerland
746394
Reviewed July 15, 2018
Great place
Through a little alley you need to go in order to find it but it’s well worth the reward. Surrounded mainly by locals and a few Korean tourists: the food was extremely good and ridiculously cheap for what we ate. You’re having local food with the locals like the locals, so no table cloth and Gault Milliau but an amazing experience and well filled stomach!
