VeronicaP792
Sydney, Australia
62
Authentic Banh Xeo
Our first experience of Banh Xeo was at Banh Xeo Ba Duong. At this time, we didn't have any expectations, and had nothing to compare it to. Nonetheless, we still found this place to be authentic, fresh, and mouth watering!!! We had several Banh Xeo's after this one, and nowhere has been anywhere near as good.
