scratchmypack
Da Nang, Vietnam
429
Reviewed June 7, 2018
Coolest Location Delicious Reputation
The location is easily missed as it’s tucked away down a local alley way, but if you look a bit lost, every local can point you in the right direction.
This place is an automatic must. The atmosphere will make you feel like a local as you sit down and they immediately bring you the best banh xeo in town-it’s all about the sauce.
Prices are great. Food is delicious. Atmosphere is unique. Definitely worth your time.
Date of visit: May 2018
