Real Food for Real People!
Keeping it real with the best Banh Xeo in Danang! Also known as sizzling cake, this is as good as it gets! The Pork Satay wrapped in rice paper is scrumptious with a load of vegetables. Off the beaten track but yet on track for the best that Vietnam offers!
