LNQuan
5616
Reviewed May 17, 2018
Best banh xeo in town
This place serves the best banh xeo (fried rice pancake) in town. They also have nem lui (pork meatball on the stick) and grilled beef. All of them are yummy but the best thing is the peanut sauce, they have their secret recipe here. A must-try when you are in Da Nang.
